    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Base type which represents blob of fixed size.</para>
<para>std::string is convenient to use but it is not safe. We can not specify the fixed length for string.</para>
<para>For std::array it is possible, so we prefer it over std::string. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
